Maintainer: Ildiko Czeller <czeildi@gmail.com>
Description: Sobriety checkpoints are designed to help ensure personal and public
    safety. Methods are provided to run "sobriety" checks on your system to ensure
    your computing environment is as safe as possible from the perspectives of
    confidentiality and integrity.
